                            <__p_inlines>Write a start XML element for this block.

Iterate through all properties of this block.

If the property is not an empty string then write it as a XML text element, using the key with an underscore appended to it as the tag.

Iterate through all children of this block and call their to XML method.

Write an end XML element.
</__p_inlines>
